  <entry>
    <title>autossh systemd</title>
    <link href="http://blog.balaleica.xyz/2016/12/11/autossh-systemd/"/>
    <id>http://blog.balaleica.xyz/2016/12/11/autossh-systemd/</id>
    <published>2016-12-11T02:16:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-12-12T01:47:35.138Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>利用 autossh 構建反向 ssh 隧道並通過 systemd 維持長久連接</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p><img src="http://7xku3r.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/hexo_2016/sshtunnel_schema.png" alt="autossh"></p>
<h2 id="場景"><a href="#場景" class="headerlink" title="場景"></a>場景</h2><p>需要從公網連接到位於內網的機器時 可以先從位於內網的 LocalServer 向公網的某臺 RelayServer<br>發起 ssh 的反連接 然後利用這個已建立的反向連接從公網連接 Localserver</p>
<blockquote>
<p>LocalServer~$ ssh -fN -R 10022:localhost:22 RelayServer_USER@RelayServer</p>
</blockquote>
<p><code>-R 10022:localhost:22</code> 定義了反向隧道 它通過 RelayServer 的 10022 端口將流量轉發到 LocalServer 的 22 端口 <code>fN</code> 参数是让 ssh 在后台运行</p>
<p>为应对不稳定网络环境 如网络拥塞以及 ssh 超时等问题 需要使用 autossh 工具维持持久连接 參數如下</p>
<blockquote>
<p>LocalServer~$ autossh -M 10900 -fN -o “PubkeyAuthentication=yes” -o “StrictHostKeyChecking=false” -o “PasswordAuthentication=no” -o “ServerAliveInterval 60” -o “ServerAliveCountMax 3” -R RelayServer:10022:localhost:22 Relayserver_USER@RelayServer</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="systemd"><a href="#systemd" class="headerlink" title="systemd"></a>systemd</h2><p>在 Arch 中通過 systemd 來控制開機自啓 service 如下</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[Unit]</div><div class="line">Description=Reverse channel to workstation</div><div class="line">Wants=network-online.target</div><div class="line">After=network.target</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">[Service]</div><div class="line">Type=simple</div><div class="line">User=[USER]</div><div class="line">Restart=always</div><div class="line">RestartSec=60</div><div class="line">ExecStart=/usr/bin/autossh -M 20000 -q -N -o &quot;ServerAliveInterval 60&quot; -o &quot;ServerAliveCountMax 3&quot; USER@RelayServer -R RelayServer:6681:localhost:22</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">[Install]</div><div class="line">WantedBy=multi-user.target</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;利用 autossh 構建反向 ssh 隧道並通過 systemd 維持長久連接&lt;/p&gt;
    
