    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Mac 上 Rime 用五筆輸出繁體字的配置</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<p><img src="https://rimeime.github.io/images/logo.png" alt="Rime"></p>
<h2 id="爲什麼是繁體"><a href="#爲什麼是繁體" class="headerlink" title="爲什麼是繁體"></a>爲什麼是繁體</h2><p>文章開頭 ，先感謝<strong>佛振</strong>大神創造了輸入法之神 Rime 實乃輸入法愛好者之福 。</p>
<p>至於爲什麼是繁體 ，李如一先生在知乎上的回答基本上囊括了所有的初衷與動機 ：</p>
<blockquote><ol>
<li>我是看簡體字長大的，而我就是不喜歡舒舒服服的。</li>
<li>It’s just a small step in the process of undoing everything the Chinese Communist Party did to us in the past several decades.</li>
</ol>
<footer><strong>不鳥萬如一</strong><cite><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/27360845/answer/46205075" target="_blank" rel="external">大陆人日常使用繁体字是一种什么心态</a></cite></footer></blockquote>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><p>Squirrel 目前的最新版本是 0.9.26.1 ，在這個版本上配置五筆的「簡入繁出」已經非常的簡單 ，無須再像以往那樣手動安裝 opencc 的庫等操作 ，只需簡單寫一下配置文件即可 。</p>
<p>簡入繁出的主要配置文件 <code>wubi_trad.schema.yaml</code> 內容如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div><div class="line">89</div><div class="line">90</div><div class="line">91</div><div class="line">92</div><div class="line">93</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Rime schema settings</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># encoding: utf-8</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">schema:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  schema_id:</span> wubi_trad</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  name:</span> 五筆·簡入繁出</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  version:</span> <span class="string">"0.6"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  author:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 發明人 王永民先生</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 輸入方案製作 佛振 &lt;chen.sst@gmail.com<span class="string">&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  description:</span> <span class="string">|</span></div><div class="line">    五筆字型86版 簡入繁出</div><div class="line">    需要安裝 opencc 簡繁轉換詞典</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dependencies:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> pinyin_simp</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">switches:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> ascii_mode</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    reset:</span> <span class="number">0</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 中文, 西文 ]</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> full_shape</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 半角, 全角 ]</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> extended_charset</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 常用, 增廣 ]</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> zh_trad</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    reset:</span> <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 简体, 繁體 ]</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> ascii_punct</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 。，, ．， ]</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">engine:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  processors:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> ascii_composer</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> recognizer</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> key_binder</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> speller</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punctuator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> selector</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> navigator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> express_editor</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  segmentors:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> ascii_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> matcher</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> abc_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punct_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> fallback_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  translators:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punct_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> reverse_lookup_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> table_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  filters:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> simplifier</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> uniquifier</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">speller:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  delimiter:</span> <span class="string">" ;'"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  max_code_length:</span> <span class="number">4</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">translator:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dictionary:</span> wubi86</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  prism:</span> wubi_trad</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  enable_charset_filter:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  disable_user_dict_for_patterns:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> <span class="string">"^z.*$"</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">abc_segmentor:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  extra_tags:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> reverse_lookup</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">reverse_lookup:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dictionary:</span> pinyin_simp</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  prefix:</span> <span class="string">"`"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  suffix:</span> <span class="string">"'"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  tips:</span> 〔拼音〕</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  preedit_format:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([nl])v/$<span class="number">1</span>ü/</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([nl])ue/$<span class="number">1</span>üe/</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([jqxy])v/$<span class="number">1</span>u/</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">simplifier:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  opencc_config:</span> s2t.json</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  option_name:</span> zh_trad</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">punctuator:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">key_binder:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">recognizer:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  patterns:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    reverse_lookup:</span> <span class="string">"`[a-z]*'?$"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>寫好了這個主要配置文件之後 ，還需要在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> 將繁體五筆輸入法寫入到已選輸入法中 ，這樣在部署的時候才能生成相關的 bin 文件 。</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="attr">customization:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  distribution_code_name:</span> Weasel</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  distribution_version:</span> <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="number">.26</span><span class="number">.1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  generator:</span> <span class="string">"Rime::SwitcherSettings"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  modified_time:</span> <span class="string">"Mon Aug 06 02:21:38 2012"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  rime_version:</span> <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="number">.2</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">patch:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  schema_list:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    - schema:</span> wubi_pinyin</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    - schema:</span> wubi_trad</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>到這裏 ，繁體五筆所需要的配置已經完成 ，部署完成就可以愉快的用 Squirrel 來寫繁體字了 。</p>
<p>不過 ，挑剔如我 ，怎麼能忍受在 <code>default.custom.yaml</code> 裏放置兩個五筆輸入法 ？平時用的是 <code>wubi_pinyin</code> 只要將 <code>wubi_pinyin.schema.yaml</code> 稍微修改一下即可 ：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Rime schema settings</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment"># encoding: utf-8</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">schema:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  schema_id:</span> wubi_pinyin</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  name:</span> <span class="string">"五笔·拼音"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  version:</span> <span class="string">"0.9"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  author:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> 發明人 王永民先生</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  description:</span> <span class="string">|</span></div><div class="line">    五筆字型86版＋漢語拼音混合輸入。</div><div class="line">    碼表源自 ibus-table</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dependencies:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> pinyin_simp</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">switches:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> extended_charset</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 常用, 增廣 ]</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  - name:</span> simplification</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    reset:</span> <span class="number">1</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    states:</span> [ 汉字, 漢字 ]</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">simplifier:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">     opencc_config:</span> s2t.json</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">engine:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  processors:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> ascii_composer</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> recognizer</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> key_binder</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> speller</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punctuator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> selector</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> navigator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> express_editor</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  segmentors:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> ascii_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> matcher</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> abc_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punct_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> fallback_segmentor</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  translators:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> punct_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> reverse_lookup_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> table_translator</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  filters:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> simplifier</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> uniquifier</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">speller:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  delimiter:</span> <span class="string">" ;'"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  max_code_length:</span> <span class="number">4</span>  <span class="comment"># 四碼頂字上屏</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">translator:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dictionary:</span> wubi86</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  prism:</span> wubi_pinyin</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  enable_charset_filter:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  enable_sentence:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  enable_encoder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  encode_commit_history:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  max_phrase_length:</span> <span class="number">4</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  disable_user_dict_for_patterns:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> <span class="string">"^z.*$"</span></div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">abc_segmentor:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  extra_tags:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> reverse_lookup</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">reverse_lookup:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  dictionary:</span> pinyin_simp</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  prefix:</span> <span class="string">"`"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  suffix:</span> <span class="string">"'"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  tips:</span> 〔拼音〕</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  preedit_format:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([nl])v/$<span class="number">1</span>ü/</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([nl])ue/$<span class="number">1</span>üe/</div><div class="line"><span class="bullet">    -</span> xform/([jqxy])v/$<span class="number">1</span>u/</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">punctuator:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">key_binder:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">recognizer:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  import_preset:</span> default</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  patterns:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">    reverse_lookup:</span> <span class="string">"`[a-z]*'?$"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>至此 ，配置完全完成 ，需要注意的是 yaml 文件的格式 。</p>
<p>Happy typing (</p>
]]></content>
    
